<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="strlen" id="strlen">strlen</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
语法：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstring&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">size_t</span> <span class="kw3">strlen</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>str <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

strlen()返回str的长度（由null终止符前的字符数量决定）。str不可以为空。
</p>

<p>
相关主题： <a href="memcpy" class="wikilink1" title="cn:c:string:memcpy">memcpy</a>, <a href="strchr" class="wikilink1" title="cn:c:string:strchr">strchr</a>, <a href="strcmp" class="wikilink1" title="cn:c:string:strcmp">strcmp</a>, <a href="strncmp" class="wikilink1" title="cn:c:string:strncmp">strncmp</a>
</p>

</div>
